<title>Ellipses</title>
<introduction>

<table>
<tabular>
<row>
<cell><p>By the end of this section, you should</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>know the geometric definition of an ellipse.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>know the meaning of the center, vertices, foci, major axis and minor axis of an ellipse.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to find equation of an ellipse whose major axis is horizontal or vertical.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to identify equations representing ellipses.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to find the center, foci and vertices of an ellipse and sketch the ellipse.</p>
</li>
</ul></cell>
</row>
</tabular>
</table>

</introduction>

